  },
  "universal_guidelines_for_main_agent": [
    "DO NOT use 'purple' or 'teal' gradients unless specifically for the 'AI Route' indicator.",
    "Mobile-First means 'Thumb-Friendly'. Primary actions must be in the bottom 50% of the screen.",
    "The Map is the hero. Ensure UI elements (Search, Sheets) obscure the map as little as possible.",
    "Use 'Lucide React' for all icons.",
    "Implement the 'Bottom Sheet' pattern for route details. It should feel physics-based (drag to dismiss).",
    "Ticket Page: Use a 'skeuomorphic-lite' design (dashed lines, cutout circles) to make tickets feel real.",
    "Live Radar: This page should switch to a Darker Map Mode to make the 'Heatmap' colors (Green/Red) pop.",
    "Ensure the app container is centered on desktop with 'max-w-md mx-auto' to simulate a mobile phone view.",
    "Install 'lucide-react' and 'react-leaflet' and 'leaflet' if not present.",
    "Use 'clsx' or 'tailwind-merge' for conditional classes.",
    "Add 'data-testid' to all interactive elements."
  ]
}